<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{exterior (approach to the needles monument) a broad canyon }
<A>__{full shot day a small pack train (nine or ten horses, six or seven men) winds through a canyon behind which we can see huge needles of rock: majestic, savage country. at the head of the column ride ethan, emilio, and martin. behind them come emilio's cargadores lean, hard bitten wiry little mexicans. one leads a handsome palomino. the sound of the castanets echoes in the musical theme.}
